@hypebeastkicks: After making a public statement in response to @nike suing @johngeigerco over the Geiger GF-01’s copyright infringement of the Air Force 1, Geiger and La La Land Production and Design Inc. have hired sneaker industry expert and lawyer Kenneth Anand to lead his team in their lawsuit with Nike. Anand currently serves as the Counsel to Jayaram Law and was Kanye West‘s former General Counsel of YEEZY Apparel and a co-creator of Sneaker Law. HYPEBEAST received an exclusive statement, swipe to check it out.⁠⁠
Photo: John Geiger
